title: Video: Kenny Jackett on Wolves clash
text:
Fulham 0 Wolves 3 - Report and pictures 
On the pitch it's been reasonably plain sailing, though, with Wednesday's 3-0 win at 10-man Fulham setting them up nicely for the weekend. 
Now comes a Sky Sports televised game at Molineux tomorrow at 12.15pm, as Kenny Jackett's players look to keep the focus on football. Receive daily email updates from the Express & Star
